00:05:04.229 --> 00:05:09.759
So this mulching here, some people would do
it after they plant instead of during the

00:05:09.759 --> 00:05:10.759
garden soil preparation.

00:05:10.759 --> 00:05:15.009
I like to do it before I plant and you can
kind of figure out what works best for you

00:05:15.009 --> 00:05:20.340
but it can be difficult to put mulch around
existing plants, it’s kind of finicky.

00:05:20.340 --> 00:05:24.909
With this, you just plop it on and it’s
pretty easy to plant in there.

00:05:24.909 --> 00:05:38.929
So I’ll get all this looking nice now and
then I’ll go onto the next video.

